## 💻 PART 2: Add the scripts

Now the magic part — the code! For each script below, follow where I tell you to
put it. To add a script: hover over the right spot in Explorer, click the **+**,
and choose **Script**. Delete anything already inside it, then paste my code.

---

### Script 1 — The Money System
**Where to put it:** inside **ServerScriptService** (find it in Explorer)

```lua
-- Gives every player a "Cash" counter on the leaderboard
game.Players.PlayerAdded:Connect(function(player)
	local leaderstats = Instance.new("Folder")
	leaderstats.Name = "leaderstats"
	leaderstats.Parent = player

	local cash = Instance.new("IntValue")
	cash.Name = "Cash"
	cash.Value = 0
	cash.Parent = leaderstats
end)
```

---

### Script 2 — The Dropper
**Where to put it:** inside your **Dropper** part
(Hover over the Dropper part in Explorer → click **+** → add a Script inside it)

```lua
local dropper = script.Parent

-- How many seconds between each drop (the Buy Button can lower this!)
dropper:SetAttribute("DropSpeed", 2)

while true do
	task.wait(dropper:GetAttribute("DropSpeed"))

	-- Make a little block
	local drop = Instance.new("Part")
	drop.Name = "Drop"
	drop.Size = Vector3.new(1, 1, 1)
	drop.Color = Color3.fromRGB(85, 255, 127)
	drop.Position = dropper.Position - Vector3.new(0, 2, 0)
	drop.Parent = workspace

	-- This block is worth 5 cash
	local cashValue = Instance.new("IntValue")
	cashValue.Name = "CashValue"
	cashValue.Value = 5
	cashValue.Parent = drop

	-- If nobody collects it in 20 seconds, remove it (keeps the game clean)
	game:GetService("Debris"):AddItem(drop, 20)
end
```

---

### Script 3 — The Collector
**Where to put it:** inside your **Collector** part

```lua
local collector = script.Parent

collector.Touched:Connect(function(hit)
	-- Only react to our dropper blocks
	if hit.Name == "Drop" then
		local cashValue = hit:FindFirstChild("CashValue")
		if cashValue then
			-- Give the cash to every player in the game
			for _, player in ipairs(game.Players:GetPlayers()) do
				local stats = player:FindFirstChild("leaderstats")
				if stats then
					stats.Cash.Value = stats.Cash.Value + cashValue.Value
				end
			end
			hit:Destroy() -- remove the block after collecting
		end
	end
end)
```

---

### Script 4 — The Buy Button
**Where to put it:** inside your **BuyButton** part

```lua
local button = script.Parent
local canBuy = true

button.Touched:Connect(function(hit)
	local player = game.Players:GetPlayerFromCharacter(hit.Parent)

	if player and canBuy then
		canBuy = false

		local stats = player:FindFirstChild("leaderstats")
		if stats and stats.Cash.Value >= 50 then
			-- Take 50 cash
			stats.Cash.Value = stats.Cash.Value - 50

			-- Make the Dropper drop TWICE as fast!
			local dropper = workspace:FindFirstChild("Dropper")
			if dropper then
				dropper:SetAttribute("DropSpeed", 1)
			end

			button.BrickColor = BrickColor.new("Bright green") -- turn green = bought!
		end

		task.wait(1) -- small pause so it doesn't buy a hundred times at once
		canBuy = true
	end
end)
```

